title: The Nativity-The Christmas Creche at the Metropolitan (Art Book)
description:
The Nativity: The Christmas Creche at the Metropolitan Museum of Art
Doubleday & Co. | 1969 | English | 70 pages | PDF | 10.7 MB

In this beautiful Christmas book, Christ's Nativity is told in the words of the King James Bible and illustrated with full color photographs of the eighteenth-century Neapolitan creche presented to The Metropolitan Museum of Art in 1964 by Loretta Hines Howard
